caption.title: Non-infectious bloodmeals prior to infectious bloodmeals do not increase dissemination rates.
caption.p: (a) Schematic of experimental design. At (b) 4, (c) 6, and (d) 9 dpi, midguts and legs were dissected from both cohorts and tested for the presence of ZIKV RNA by RT-q-PCR. ( ●) single feed; ( ●) double feed. Data were analyzed by Two-sided Fisher’s exact test. Sample sizes (represented as a fraction of positive samples/ total samples) for each treatment/ timepoint are embedded in the figures above each experimental group. Center values represent the proportion and error bars represent the binomial SE of sample proportions.
